<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>500 - Terjadi Kesalahan Server</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body { font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; background-color: #f3f4f6; color: #1f2937; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; height: 100vh; margin: 0; }
        .error-card { background: white; padding: 40px; border-radius: 12px; box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); text-align: center; max-width: 400px; width: 100%; }
        .error-code { font-size: 72px; font-weight: 700; color: #10b981; margin: 0; line-height: 1; }
        .error-title { font-size: 24px; font-weight: 600; margin: 16px 0 8px; }
        .error-desc { color: #6b7280; margin-bottom: 24px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5; }
        .back-btn { display: inline-block; background: #10b981; color: white; text-decoration: none; padding: 10px 24px; border-radius: 8px; font-weight: 600; transition: background 0.3s; }
        .back-btn:hover { background: #059669; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="error-card">
        <div style="margin-bottom: 20px;">
            <svg width="64" height="64" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#10b981" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                <path d="M10.29 3.86L1.82 18a2 2 0 0 0 1.71 3h16.94a2 2 0 0 0 1.71-3L13.71 3.86a2 2 0 0 0-3.42 0z"></path>
                <line x1="12" y1="9" x2="12" y2="13"></line>
                <line x1="12" y1="17" x2="12.01" y2="17"></line>
            </svg>
        </div>
        <h1 class="error-code">500</h1>
        <h2 class="error-title">Terjadi Kesalahan Server</h2>
        <p class="error-desc">Maaf, ada masalah di pihak kami. Silakan coba beberapa saat lagi.</p>
        <a href="/" class="back-btn">Kembali ke Beranda</a>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
